data.description: Former Messina Model with a pool located on Model Row in the Siena Lakes section of Venetian Isles. This home is customized in many ways including a double door entry to the primary BR, Sliding Glass doors from primary bedroom leading to a kidney shaped pool, oversized patio and completely fenced yard. and accordion shutters.  The primary bath features dual sinks. The kitchen features 42'' wood cabinets with the corner cabinet feature. The wall between the den and living room is partially opened and gives a beautiful spacious feeling. There is custom crown molding and wainscoting thruout the home. The closets are outfitted. The A/C is 2017 and the HWH is 2022. You'll be impressed by this property both inside and out.
